{"id": 3100, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得生活中的哪些方面被 AI 接管是可以接受的？", "description": "有哪些事情是你愿意主动交给 AI，而不担心它会过度干预你的生活的？（题图来自：iStock ©️gmast3r ）", "record_count": 6893, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201912222314097q91iaHn24wljNGb.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-12-22T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6136, "title": "你觉得生活中的哪些方面被 AI 接管是可以接受的？", "content": "你觉得生活中的哪些方面被 AI 接管是可以接受的？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 351043, "content": "打游戏，帮我完成跟剧情无关的打怪操作", "image": "img/option/option/20191222231554q7Yi8RONah54xUfw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351044, "content": "社交，设置智能社交时段，回复不想回的消息", "image": "img/option/option/20191222231743irc087wuRtxHPIJv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351045, "content": "开车，至少能帮我倒车入库把车停好", "image": "img/option/option/20191222234012CwAE5flogVmJiGP3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351046, "content": "工作，比如写周报之类的重复劳动", "image": "img/option/option/20191222232049ICR1DPyToj5eJN0g.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351047, "content": "拿主意，解决中午吃啥/衣服买啥颜色一类的难题", "image": "img/option/option/20191222232259voXAK5ZhtlYIx3iU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351048, "content": "管账，帮我理财，提醒我本月还能花多少", "image": "img/option/option/20191222234051b37VfNGLv6HtJxY1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351049, "content": "追星，打卡签到之类的交给它就好", "image": "img/option/option/20191223184047wKQaAu0yEUbg9qOS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351051, "content": "收纳，垃圾分类/整理家务不用自己花心思", "image": "img/option/option/20191222235057ev0Bko4flx6CTJyD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351050, "content": "还有其他想法/不需要任何AI，我自己来吧", "image": "img/option/option/20191222234233d7bKHSp4WthBCcXG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}